        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half and tear your <strong>bread roll[s] </strong>into large bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
