      "instruction": "<p>Whilst everything’s cooking, combine your <strong>Dijon</strong> <strong>mustard </strong>with your <strong>cider vinegar</strong>, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>in a small bowl</p><p>Mix everything together – this is your<strong> tangy mustard dressing</strong></p>",
