    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then add your <strong>green beans</strong> to a pot with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, then cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min or until tender</p><p>Once done, drain, then set aside for serving</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
